    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a portion of the Policy Information Base (PIB) for a device implementing the IP Security Architecture. The provisioning classes defined here provide control of IPsec policy. These provisioning classes can be used with other non-IPsec provisioning classes (defined in other PIB modules) to provide for a comprehensive policy controlled mapping of service requirement to device capability and usage.</t>
